fields.name: Roti and Potato Garlic Sabji
fields.description: Soft, warm, and freshly made, Roti is a classic Indian flatbread crafted from whole wheat flour, water, and a pinch of salt. Cooked on a hot griddle until lightly charred, it's puffed and golden  simple, healthy, and perfect for scooping up rich curries and flavorful sabjis. With its soft texture and earthy aroma, Roti complements any Indian meal and is a staple on every traditional thali.

fields.name: Italian Pizza
fields.description: A Taste of Italy Our classic Italian masterpiece begins with a crust that yields with a satisfying crunch, baked to golden perfection. A fragrant base of sun-ripened tomato sauce, simmered with herbs, provides the foundation. Next, a generous blanket of creamy, bubbling mozzarella, stretching with every bite. Fresh basil leaves, glistening with olive oil, are scattered across the canvas, their vibrant aroma intermingling with the savory cheese. The result: a symphony of textures and tastes, transporting you directly to a sun-drenched pizzeria in Naples. Buon appetito!
